<section id="faq" class="faq section">
  <div class="faq-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-badge">Support</div>
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p>Find answers to common questions about Cheese Chompers 3D</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-container">
      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>What is Cheese Chompers 3D?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>Cheese Chompers 3D is a browser-based knockout game where players control rats in a battle to push opponents off a floating arena. It features physics-based gameplay with simple controls but chaotic and entertaining outcomes. The game is a modification of Crazy Cattle 3D, replacing the original animals with rats and featuring a redesigned interface and sound system. Developed using Unity WebGL technology, it offers instant play without downloads, making it perfect for quick gaming sessions.</p>
            <div class="answer-tag">Game Overview</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>Is Cheese Chompers 3D free to play?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>Yes, Cheese Chompers 3D is completely free to play directly in your web browser without requiring any downloads or installations. Just visit our website, click 'Play Now,' and jump into the cheesy chaos immediately!</p>
            <div class="answer-highlight">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
              </svg>
              <span>100% Free - No Downloads Required</span>
            </div>
            <div class="answer-tag">Pricing</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>What are the controls for Cheese Chompers 3D?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>The controls for Cheese Chompers 3D are simple:</p>
            <div class="controls-grid">
              <div class="control-item">
                <div class="control-key">WASD</div>
                <div class="control-desc">Move your rat character in all directions across the platform</div>
              </div>
              <div class="control-item">
                <div class="control-key">Space</div>
                <div class="control-desc">Hold to jump and perform aerial maneuvers</div>
              </div>
              <div class="control-item">
                <div class="control-key">Mid-Air</div>
                <div class="control-desc">Perform flips during jumps for temporary speed boosts</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="answer-tag">Controls</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>Can I play Cheese Chompers 3D on mobile devices?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>Currently, Cheese Chompers 3D is primarily optimized for desktop browser play (HTML5/WebGL). Mobile support may vary depending on your device capabilities. For the best experience, we recommend playing on a computer with a keyboard for proper control.</p>
