      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>How many players can play Cheese Chompers 3D?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>While Cheese Chompers 3D doesn't display the exact number of opponents, you'll compete against multiple AI or real players depending on the game session. The arena is always bustling with activity, creating a chaotic and fun environment.</p>
            <div class="answer-tag">Gameplay</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>Is Cheese Chompers 3D related to Crazy Cattle 3D?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>Yes, Cheese Chompers 3D is a modification of Crazy Cattle 3D, replacing the original animals with rats and featuring a redesigned interface and sound system while maintaining similar core gameplay mechanics. If you enjoy Cheese Chompers 3D, you might also like other games in the series like Crazy Sheep 3D and Crazy Chicken 3D.</p>
            <div class="related-games">
              <div class="related-game">Crazy Cattle 3D</div>
              <div class="related-game">Crazy Sheep 3D</div>
              <div class="related-game">Crazy Chicken 3D</div>
            </div>
            <div class="answer-tag">Game Series</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="700">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>Are there different maps in Cheese Chompers 3D?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>Currently, Cheese Chompers 3D features one main arena map. The game is still in active development, so additional maps may be added in future updates. Despite having just one map, the unpredictable physics and chaotic gameplay ensure that each match feels unique and entertaining.</p>
            <div class="development-status">
              <div class="status-label">Development Status:</div>
              <div class="status-badge">Active Development</div>
            </div>
            <div class="answer-tag">Maps & Content</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="800">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <div class="question-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-0.5-5h1v-1h-1v1zm1.5-9c-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4h2c0-1.1 0.9-2 2-2s2 0.9 2 2c0 2-3 1.75-3 5h2c0-2.25 3-2.5 3-5 0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>Is Cheese Chompers 3D suitable for all ages?</span>
          <div class="arrow-icon">
            <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="answer-content">
            <p>Absolutely! Cheese Chompers 3D is family-friendly and perfect for players of all ages. The game features cartoon-style physics with no violent content, making it appropriate for younger players while still being entertaining for adults. The intuitive controls and whimsical presentation make it accessible to everyone, while the physics-based gameplay offers depth for more experienced players.</p>
            <div class="answer-highlight">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Family-Friendly Gaming</span>
            </div>
            <div class="answer-tag">Audience</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-more">
      <div class="more-questions">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M20 2H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 22l4-4h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 12h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V6h2v4z"/>
        </svg>
        <p>Still have questions? Feel free to visit our <a href="https://github.com/cheesechompers-3d/cheesechompers-3d" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">GitHub repository</a>!</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#game" class="btn btn-play-now">Play Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 20%, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.05) 0%, transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(140, 82, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 30%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-quaternary), var(--color-tertiary));
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-quaternary), var(--color-tertiary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .section-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 42, 64, 0.7), rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.7));
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-hover);
    border-color: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.2);
  }

  .faq-question {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-white);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .question-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.2), rgba(140, 82, 255, 0.1));
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: var(--color-quaternary);
    margin-right: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .faq-question:hover .question-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(10deg);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.3);
  }

  .arrow-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .faq-icon {
    transition: transform var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .faq-question.active {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 42, 64, 0.9), rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.9));
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .faq-question.active .question-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-quaternary), var(--color-tertiary));
    color: var(--color-white);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.3);
  }

  .faq-question.active .faq-icon {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 42, 64, 0.5), rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.5));
  }

  .faq-answer.active {
    padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    max-height: 1000px;
  }

  .answer-content {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .faq-answer p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .answer-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-quaternary);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.2);
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .answer-highlight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background-color: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.1);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-quaternary);
  }

  .answer-highlight svg {
    color: var(--color-quaternary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .answer-highlight span {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .controls-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .control-item {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.1);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .control-item:hover {
